We have many trees on the property, and stones. We\'re planning on saving our seeds and having a winter harvest with a movable hoop house and row covers. The idea is to feed two families year-round, and to plant a row for the hungry as well (food pantry). Next year we\'ll add berry bushes, dwarf fruit trees and "edible forest garden" crops.
